      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c77cbddd5cd4c3232f650a4"
      },
      "index": 1,
      "text": "That doesn't surprise me too much. We haven't actually gotten a smoking gun on this case. And with the amount of rumors flying through on such a crisis situation, we just weren't too convincing.\n\nPlus the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAntithesisCreed],Creed]] ideology is shared by many government officials. Most likely the ones who freed him are in league with the Inheritors.",
      "branches": [
