    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cce9240fc2df1149bece2dd"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "And are we forgetting who we were dealing with in the first place? \n\nProfessor Bambo claimed the Inheritors were behind the ghost 'Mechs being used to disperse the nerve agent based solely on data correlation. I wouldn't put much stock on his <i>scientific</i> work since this evidence is circumstantial at best.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 3,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
