    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c4dcb6a25a31217295ec360"
      },
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, this is the guy who also believes in 'Mech HPG portals. I've been reading his stuff lately and that Inheritor story might be a fabrication as well.\n\n I was too ready to believe him, we should have paid more attention to Dr. Murad.",
      "branches": [
