    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c5d66724cadad7c4c1c67fe"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "A patient zero for the original variant of the Death's Mask is a most likely probability, but I doubt Bambo was solely responsible. \n\nI've been going through Lord Karosas' reports and there are also other systems that he didn't visit with recent [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LorePeripheryPox],plague]] outbreaks and no records of ghost 'Mechs involved. So he definitely cherry-picked the data to fit his claims. Something or someone else was also at work here. We may never know.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 6,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
