      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cccf08119bd33cf720bd37b"
      },
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Or, perhaps both Bambo and the Inheritors were involved on it, and now they're blaming one another. \n\nI've also heard references to this being an [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreInnerSphere],Inner Sphere]] covert attack on the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LorePeriphery],Periphery]]. They're likely just rumors, but that kind of gossip spreads like wildfire on a dry prairie in this location of space. ",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 7,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
