      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cce2342ee82b2a78d97d99c"
      },
      "index": 7,
      "text": "We, like everyone else, just don't know what's really happening. \n\nLooks like we can't do much about it at this point, so let's all brace for the epidemic to pass through us. ",
